name: 🚀GSE🌏
description:
You are returning home from an off planet mission, you are almost out of fuel and only have enough in the tanks to one final boost, use it wisely

HOW TO

Get Home without hitting the dead planets.

A&D To decrease & increase launch POWER.

W&S To move UP & DOWN.

E&R To ROTATE.

"Space" To Fire.

See how short you can make your path.

Made for the Jamingtons Game Jam http://www.oneratgames.com/jam...

Made by: Dylan J. Walker
